  <div style=3D"display: none; max-height: 0px; overflow: hidden;">Welcome =
back to What I=E2=80=99m Hearing, officially on the holiday party circuit. =
At Tuesday=E2=80=99s Warner Discovery thing at Tower Bar, I was relieved to=
 learn from C.E.O. David Zaslav that he=E2=80=99s finally finished his five=
